OL,3,CChloe Malle to succeed Anna Wintour as
OL,4,Chead of US Vogue
OL,6,FChloe Malle has been named the new
OL,7,Fhead of editorial content at American
OL,8,FVogue after Dame Anna Wintour stepped
OL,9,Fdown from her role as the day-to-day
OL,10,Feditor of the title.
OL,12,FDame Anna will remain in charge of
OL,13,FVogue globally - which includes 28
OL,14,Feditions - and as chief content
OL,15,Fofficer of the media company Conde
OL,16,FNast, which oversees prominent media
OL,17,Fbrands including Vogue, Vanity Fair
OL,18,Fand GQ.
