OL,3,CChloe Malle to succeed Anna Wintour as
OL,4,Chead of US Vogue
OL,6,FShe will now lead the creative and
OL,7,Feditorial direction of the title and
OL,8,Fjoin Vogue's ten existing heads of
OL,9,Feditorial content around the world,
OL,10,Freporting to Dame Anna.
OL,12,FMalle said fashion and media "are both
OL,13,Fevolving at breakneck speed," and she
OL,14,Fis "so thrilled and awed" to be part
OL,15,Fof that.
OL,17,F"I also feel incredibly fortunate to
OL,18,Fstill have Anna just down the hall as
OL,19,Fmy mentor," she added.
