OL,3,CChloe Malle to succeed Anna Wintour as
OL,4,Chead of US Vogue
OL,6,FThe 39-year-old studied at Brown
OL,7,FUniversity in the US and has two
OL,8,Fchildren.
OL,10,FAnnouncing the appointment, Dame Anna
OL,11,Fsaid: "Fashion is the art of embracing
OL,12,Fchange, but some changes run closer to
OL,13,Fone's heart than the rest.
OL,15,F"When it came to hiring someone to
OL,16,Fedit American Vogue, letting me turn
OL,17,Fmy attention more intensely to Vogue's
OL,18,Fmultifaceted growth across its global
OL,19,Faudiences and publications and events
OL,20,Flike the Met Gala and Vogue World, I
OL,21,Fknew I had one chance to get it right.
