OL,3,CChloe Malle to succeed Anna Wintour as
OL,4,Chead of US Vogue
OL,6,F"I'm thrilled to announce that Chloe
OL,7,FMalle will be the next head of
OL,8,Feditorial content for our US title,
OL,9,Fleading the American magazine and
OL,10,Fguiding its digital coverage.
OL,12,F"She's a voracious, engaged journalist
OL,13,Fwith an intuition for women's changing
OL,14,Finterests now ` and her eye for the
OL,15,Fdefinitive image is exceptional.
