OL,3,CChloe Malle to succeed Anna Wintour as
OL,4,Chead of US Vogue
OL,6,F"Chloe has long been one of Vogue's
OL,7,Fsecret weapons when it comes to
OL,8,Ftracking fashion. But she is not so
OL,9,Fburied in the industry that she misses
OL,10,Fthe world: like the best designers,
OL,11,Fshe understands fashion's big picture,
OL,12,Fits role shaping not just what's on
OL,13,Fthe runway but the changing fabric of
OL,14,Fmodern life."
OL,16,FThe news that Malle got the job comes
OL,17,Fahead of the latest round of shows at
OL,18,FNew York Fashion Week, starting next
OL,19,Fweek, and amid the Venice Film
OL,20,FFestival, which includes a new
OL,21,Fdocumentary about her father.
